6 (3) A peer support session is confidential, and, EXCEPT AS PROVIDED IN SUBSECTION (2)(I), a qualified
7 peer supporter in a local first responder peer support program is prohibited from providing testimony about a
8 peer support session, including individual and group peer support sessions.
